cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV 

This paper deals with clustering algorithms and their performance on different datasets, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of heuristics and optimization techniques, which are relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the datasets used in the experiments include image datasets such as MNIST and CIFAR, which are relevant to computer vision (cs.CV).
